{"tid":1666850,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(行動post)請真正俾外國人Stand with HongKong","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T08:50:10.000Z","uid":264246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ee5934dc6eaf334673b5540d253f533ae87ac7","tid":1666850,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"有人問點樣令外國人真正Stand with HongKong<br />\n請將罷買中資,抵制中資貨,同埋唔好黎香港或者中國旅遊作宣傳到全球<br />\n令佢地真係可以Stand with HongKong<br />\n<br />\n同埋若果有人識design可以design一個簡單少少既logo去代表抵制呢個中資品牌<br />\n等若果有想裝修既兄弟可以做完直接噴上/貼上logo<br />\n等行動更容易清楚明白亦慳文宣組好多功夫<br />\n<br />\n最後我亦知其實國際線人手好緊拙,因為太多人剩係等運到乜都唔做<br />\n但我相信如果上述野做左會幫輕你地好多去解釋裝修背後既原因<br />\n<br />\n但我真係幫唔到手,因為我識既英文真係好有限,開左twitter都真係望到d英文都頭痛<br />\n如果見到希望幫到大家<br />\n<br />\n#Fight for Freedom<br />\n#Stand with HongKong<br />\n#Boycott China"},{"pid":"2fb9e064216789f9a41cca66b81ee99a76222a3e","tid":1666850,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e5cdd4d2b55da0ba7540c2da61fd6b9f157e50f","tid":1666850,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9297fd12cc7974cfd173d9456e0bbe2f533a8f33","tid":1666850,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b0f8f10a3bd175e9ef5e448b0ea50f388986358","tid":1666850,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f94d4def3ffdb0ec1ac107417c793aca73225b4","tid":1666850,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d6b21b116b4499b3f4cbff62fff6fde701cc4a6","tid